---
// Agentic AI narrative progression: Generative → Practical → Trusted → Agentic
---

<div class="ans-grid">
  <div class="ans-stage">
    <div class="ans-stage-header">
      <span class="ans-num">01</span>
      <h3 class="ans-title">Generative AI</h3>
    </div>
    <p class="ans-question">What can AI create?</p>
    <p class="ans-desc">The market question was possibility. Could AI write, summarise, translate, generate? The answer was yes — faster and cheaper than expected. The editorial task was to calm the hype and give organisations practical guidance.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="ans-connector" aria-hidden="true">→</div>

  <div class="ans-stage">
    <div class="ans-stage-header">
      <span class="ans-num">02</span>
      <h3 class="ans-title">Agentic AI</h3>
    </div>
    <p class="ans-question">Can AI complete meaningful work on our behalf?</p>
    <p class="ans-desc">The vision argument came early — before the technology fully arrived. Where was generative AI heading? Towards autonomous execution: agents that monitor, decide and act without being prompted at each step.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="ans-connector" aria-hidden="true">→</div>

  <div class="ans-stage">
    <div class="ans-stage-header">
      <span class="ans-num">03</span>
      <h3 class="ans-title">Practical AI</h3>
    </div>
    <p class="ans-question">How can businesses use it today?</p>
    <p class="ans-desc">With the vision established, the market needed implementation. Domain-specific models, embedded workflows, real adoption evidence. For finance and accounting, 25,000 professionals using Copilot daily and MTD as structural catalyst.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="ans-connector" aria-hidden="true">→</div>

  <div class="ans-stage ans-stage--current">
    <div class="ans-stage-header">
      <span class="ans-num">04</span>
      <h3 class="ans-title">Trusted AI</h3>
    </div>
    <p class="ans-question">Can we trust it with data, decisions and workflows?</p>
    <p class="ans-desc">As adoption deepened, governance became the central question. Authentic Intelligence — domain-specific AI with transparent training, human accountability and professional standards — became the differentiating argument.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .ans-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .ans-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  .ans-connector {
    display: none;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.5;
    padding: 1.5rem 0.5rem 0;
    align-self: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .ans-connector {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  .ans-stage {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--color-surface-secondary);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.625rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .ans-stage {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
  }

  .ans-stage--current {
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 35%, transparent);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 6%, var(--color-surface));
  }

  .ans-stage-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .ans-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .ans-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ans-question {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .ans-desc {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-ink-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
